      "paragraphs": [
        "```bash python3 -m daily_pipeline.cli \\ --team <team-a.json> \\ --team <team-b.json> \\ --output-root tmp/daily-pipeline ```",
        "- `--teams-file` - `--config` - `--trigger team-create|team-update` - `--allow-degraded` - `--dry-run`",
        "```bash python3 -m daily_pipeline.cli \\ --sync \\ --root \"$VK_ROOT\" \\ --build-team-py \"$BUILD_TEAM_PY\" \\ --post-audit ```",
        "- `--root` (defaults to `$VK_ROOT` or `.`) - `--build-team-py` - `--post-audit` - `--dry-run`",
        "- Routing is separated between team-mode and sync-mode behavior. - Parser exclusivity is enforced for `--team` and `--sync`. - `--teams-file` is a team-mode input and is not consumed in sync-mode execution."
